_aChangeLog.text: Reworked hostage rescue points
Increased a max number of players from 6v8 to 10v11
Bots AI has been improved
Removed most garbage from streets
Removed access to T Spawn which allowed CT to directly go there and changed access to storage room
Added trees & grass with benches
Hostages are now in different places (they are no longer in one place)
Reworked room with vent
Changed building textures
Reworked storage room (added some storages)
Fixed a bug with grates near CT Spawn which prevented bullets to go through them
Added a new building with accessible roof through ladder
Added small building (with one hostage) located near T Spawn
Added vent from CT Side to access building
Added a place from T Side which requires time to break grate and access
Added clipping on stairs in building
Entry to storage room through boxes is now only accessible from T Side (there is no possiblity to go back in the same way)

_sText:
A 10v11 hostage rescue map. The terrorists told the hostages not to move from their position because otherwise they will be killed. But is it really true using the Counter-Terrorists force?

Counter-Terrorists Objective (CT's): Rescue 5 hostages or kill all terrorists (T's).

Terrorists Objective (T's): Prevent the hostages from being rescued or kill all Counter-Terrorists (CT's).
